Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Northridge 80|35--Des Moines’ Premier Industrial and Logistics Center being developed at the crossroads of the US in Central Iowa.  Fronting Interstate 80 & 35, stretching from New York to Los Angeles and from Canada to Mexico, this location provides an excellent ready to build site for companies delivery goods and services to much of the country.  Northridge 80|35 is designed for multiple sized occupiers seeking facilities with immediate access to the greater population of Des Moines and under 6 hours access to Chicago, Minneapolis, St. Louis, Kansas City and Omaha.
